data.rationale:
This is the RIPE RPSL Object Library (RPSL-OL), a set of routines
    for parsing and manipulating RPSL objects.

    This library is included in the RIPE Whois Server, and is used by
    that software, so applications that use this API are insured maximum
    compatibility. However, this release is separate and there are no
    dependencies.
